TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct dbms_lob.getlength(LC."XML_DATA") as VariableSize, LUX.USER_NAME as LastModifiedUser, LC."NAME" as VariableName, LS."NAME" as SnapshotName, LP."NAME" as ApplicationName, LP.IS_SYSTEM IsSystem, LP.IS_TOOLKIT IsToolkit from LSW_CLASS LC, LSW_USR_XREF LUX, LSW_PO_VERSIONS LPV, LSW_PROJECT LP, LSW_SNAPSHOT LS where LUX.USER_ID = LC.LAST_MODIFIED_BY_USER_ID and dbms_lob.getlength(LC."XML_DATA") > ? and LC.VERSION_ID = LPV.PO_VERSION_ID and LS.BRANCH_ID = LPV.BRANCH_ID and LS.PROJECT_ID = LP.PROJECT_ID order by dbms_lob.getlength(LC."XML_DATA") desc
